examples.en: His wallet was bulging with banknotes.
His pockets were bulging with candy.
The squirrel's cheeks were bulging with nuts.
He fell heavily to the floor, his eyes bulging wide with fear.
examples.ru: Он тяжело упал на пол, вытаращив глаза от страха.

examples.en: More and more men use pochettes to avoid bulging their trousers.
examples.ru: Все больше мужчин пользуются барсетками, чтобы не вытягивать карманы брюк.
